Theo_James http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Theo_James 0 Theodore Peter James Kinnaird Taptiklis (born 16 December 1984) is an English actor, director, producer and model, known for portraying the role of Tobias "Four" Eaton in The Divergent Series film trilogy. He played Detective Walter William Clark, Jr. in the crime-drama series Golden Boy (2013), and David in the films Underworld: Awakening (2012) and Underworld: Blood Wars (2016). He starred as Will Younger in the Netflix Original film How It Ends (2018).In 2015, he became the brand ambassador for Hugo Boss fragrances for men, appearing in print ads and commercials.James runs a film and TV production company Untapped along with Andrew D. Corkin of Uncorked Productions.
